rows.label: qst701003_msg0001
rows.name:
Aye, I know Morumo. But even if I
wanted to help you, which I don't,
I couldn't.

rows.label: qst701003_msg0002
rows.name:
Won't help nobody who helped them
as ran away from the capital. Not even
Prince Adel, begging your pardon.

rows.label: qst701003_msg0003
rows.name:
You run around telling people what
they want to hear, but you don't have
no interest in actually protecting us.

rows.label: qst701003_msg0004
rows.name:
People as want to save everyone end
up saving no-one. That's where you're
headed, mark my words.

rows.label: qst701003_msg0005
rows.name:
There, I've said my piece.
Get off home.

rows.label: qst701003_msg0101
rows.name:
People as want to save everyone end
up saving no-one. That's where you're
headed, mark my words.

rows.label: qst701003_msg0102
rows.name:
There, I've said my piece.
Get off home.

rows.label: qst701003_msg0201
rows.name:
It's what I asked for, all right.
See you take care of the rest, too.

rows.label: qst701003_msg0202
rows.name:
I'll get this shelter designed
in the meantime.
